      "content": "it's not just \"feeling heavy.\" it's like the light has been switched off permanently. if the artist is dead, then what's even the point of the person who's left? i look in the mirror and i don't even see a human being anymore, just this empty vessel that keeps breathing by accident. it feels so pointless.",
